##DESCRIPTION
##  Algebra problem: describe transformation from formula
##ENDDESCRIPTION

##KEYWORDS('algebra', 'function', 'graph', 'translation')

## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Functions)
## DBsection(Domain and range)
## Date('9/8/2018')
## Author('Yoshiwara')
